WHEREAS STORAGE IS DESIGNED TO ENABLE PRODUCTS TO BE WITHDRAWN TEMPORARILY FROM A MARKET SUFFERING DISEQUILIBRIUM WITH A VIEW TO THEIR RESALE AS SOON AS THE MARKET SITUATION HAS IMPROVED; WHEREAS, ACCORDINGLY, PRODUCTS STORED MUST BE SUITABLE, ACCORDING TO CASE, FOR HUMAN OR ANIMAL CONSUMPTION;
